    "pathway_type": "inflammatory",
    "description": "Central inflammatory pathway activated by TLR4 (LPS), cytokines, UV, and oxidative stress. NF-κB translocates to nucleus driving transcription of TNF-α, IL-1β, IL-6, IL-17. Key driver of acne, psoriasis, eczema, rosacea, and accelerated aging.",
