    "name": "Collagen Breakdown (MMPs)",
    "pathway_type": "structural",
    "description": "Matrix metalloproteinases (MMP-1, MMP-3, MMP-9) degrade collagen types I and III under stimulation by cortisol, UV, inflammation, and AGEs. Primary mechanism of photoaging, wrinkle formation, skin thinning, and impaired wound healing.",
