      "MMP-1 (collagenase - cleaves collagen I/III)",
      "MMP-3 (stromelysin - activates MMP-1)",
      "MMP-9 (gelatinase - basement membrane degradation)",
      "AP-1 transcription factor (MMP upregulation)"
    ],
    "activators": [
